data.description: Live your best life in this meticulously maintained 1st floor corner condo, located in a quiet community that offers all the luxuries anyone could want. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with 2 patios, offers upgrades such as crown molding throughout, granite counter tops with lovely stone backsplash in kitchen, custom built-ins, closet organizers, RainSoft, & gleaming hardwood floors and freshly painted throughout with neutral cream color. 2 car garage, Trane HVAC 2015, gas water heater 2017, 2 new garage door openers. Spacious bedrooms and HUGE PBR walk-in closet. Ceiling storage racks, screened sliding door and shelves in garage. Kitchen TV conveys. Curtains in PBR and office do not convey, all other window treatments convey. Condo Dues include Master Insurance, Exterior ground maint., Water/Sewer and Trash p/u. Pet Restrictions 1 dog <30 lbs, or 2 cats. POA Dues for clubhouse/Fitness Cntr. Pool $330/year. Make your appointment today to see this beautiful home!
